        <script>
         $(document).ready(function () {
             $("#q1, .subscribe-submit").on("click", function () {
                 InitNewsletterSubscriptionForm();
             });
 
             $(".btn-next").on("click", function () {
                 NewsletterSignupCallback.PerformCallback();
             });
 
             $(".questions input").on("keyup", function (e) {
                 if (e.keyCode === 13) {
                     NewsletterSignupCallback.PerformCallback();
                 }
             });
         });
 
         // Init newsletter subscription form.
         function InitNewsletterSubscriptionForm() {
 
             $("#NewsletterSignup").addClass("active");
             setTimeout(function () {
                 $("html, body").animate({ scrollTop: $(document).height() }, 3000);
             }, 300);
 
             if ($(".subscribe-submit").hasClass("subscribe-inited") === false) {
 
                 NewsletterSignupData.Set("step", 1);
 
                 $(".subscribe-submit").html("");
                 $(".subscribe-submit").css("padding", "0px");
                 $(".subscribe-submit").addClass("subscribe-inited");
                 setTimeout(function () {
                     $(".btn-next").addClass("subscribe-next");
                     $(".subscribe-bar").css("opacity", 1);
                     $(".subscribe-paging").css("opacity", 1);
                     $(".subscribe-pager").css("opacity", 1);
 
                 }, 800);
                 ProcessNewsletterSubscriptionStep();
                 Subscriber_Email.SetFocus();
 
             }
         }
 
         function ProcessNewsletterSubscriptionStep() {
             var nextQ = $(".questions .current").index() + 1;
 
             NewsletterSignupData.Set("step", nextQ);
 
             if (nextQ < 6) {
                 $(".subscribe-progress").css("width", parseInt($(".questions .current").index() * 20) + "%");
                 $(".questions .current").removeClass("current");
                 $(".questions li:eq(" + nextQ + ")").addClass("current");
                 $(".questions").addClass("show-next");
                 $(".subscribe-paging .current").removeClass("current");
                 $(".subscribe-paging li:eq(" + (nextQ - 1) + ")").addClass("current");
                 $(".subscribe-paging").addClass("show-next");
                 setTimeout(function () {
                     $(".questions").removeClass("show-next");
                     $(".subscribe-paging").removeClass("show-next");
                     $(".questions .current input").focus();
                 }, 200);
             } else {
                 $(".subscribe-form").fadeOut(300, function () {
                     $(".subscribe-complete").fadeIn();
                 });
                 NewsletterSignupCallback.PerformCallback();
             }
 
         }
 
         function handleNewsletterSignupCallbackComplete(s, e) {
 
             // Parse response.
             var response = JSON.parse(e.result);
 
             // Display notification.
             if (response.dialogs.notification.display === true) {
                 DisplayNotificationDalog(response.dialogs.notification.text, response.dialogs.notification.type);
                 return false;
             }
             if (response.dialogs.confirmation.display === true) {
                 DisplayConfirmationDialog(response.dialogs.confirmation.title, response.dialogs.confirmation.text, response.dialogs.confirmation.type, eval(response.dialogs.confirmation.callbackhandler));
                 return false;
             }
 
             // Go to next step if validated.
             if (response.properties.status !== 1) {
                 ProcessNewsletterSubscriptionStep();
             }
 
         }
 
         function RedirectToExtranet(s, e) {
             ExecuteNavigationTab('/extranet/abonnementen.aspx')
         }
 
         function handleFooterSubscribeClick(s, e) {
             
         }
        </script>

    <script>
     $(document).ready(function () {
 
         $(".feedback-button").on("click", function () {
 
             DisplayCustomDialogByClass('feedback-dialog');
 
         });
 
         $(".feedback-dialog").on("click", ".button", function () {
 
             if ($(this).hasClass("submitting")) {
                 return false;
             }
 
             $(this).addClass("submitting");
             FeedbackCallback.PerformCallback('submit');
         });
 
     });
 
     function handleFeedbackComplete(s, e) {
 
         // Parse response.
         var response = JSON.parse(e.result);
 
         // Close dialog if success.
         if (response.dialogs.notification.type === 0) {
             CloseConfirmationDialogs();
             setTimeout(function () {
                 Feedback_Email.SetValue('');
                 Feedback_Text.SetValue('');
             }, 500);
         }
 
         // Display notification.
         handleDialogs(response.dialogs);
 
         // Clear button.
         $(".feedback-dialog .button").removeClass("submitting");
 
     }
    </script>
